verbose_text: CLP and CLP+ PBS group had significantly increased levels of TNF-alpha, IL-1beta and IL-6, whereas treatment with rmMFG-E8 inhibited the overproduction of TNF-alpha, IL-1beta and IL-6 (TNF-alpha : 50.81 +/-0.7 vs. 149.4 +/-1.2, p < 0.01; IL-1beta : 150.64 +/-1.3 vs. 845.9 +/-16.89, p < 0.01; and IL-6 : 3505 +/- 29.96 vs. 2570 +/- 69.42, p < 0.01) (XREF_FIG).
